sentences: Maistre Guibert Kaukesel or Hubert Chaucesel (fl. c.  1230–55) was a trouvère from Arras, where he is named as a canon in a document of the Cathédrale Notre-Dame in 1250.
Maistre Guibert Kaukesel or Hubert Chaucesel (fl. c.  1230–55) was a trouvère from Arras, where he is named as a canon in a document of the Cathédrale Notre-Dame in 1250.
